fr.aumgn.bukkitutils.glob

Interface GlobPattern<T>


  • public interface GlobPattern<T>
    GlobPattern interface. To build a glob pattern you should use the builder class Glob. A GlobPattern is defined from a string which can contains special matching sequence:
    • "*" (wildcard): Matches any number of any characters.
    • "?": Matches any character.
    • "[abc]" (characters class): Matches all given characters
    • "[^abc] (inverted characters class): Matches all characters except the given one
